import React from 'react'; import { usePlayerStore } from '../store/playerStore'; const Dashboard: React.FC = () => { const { stats, filteredPlayers } = usePlayerStore(); if (!stats) { return null; } // Helper function to safely format numbers const formatNumber = (value: number | undefined | null, decimals: number = 1) => { if (value === undefined || value === null) return '0.0'; return value.toFixed(decimals); }; return (

Dashboard

{/* Key Statistics */}

Total Players

{stats.totalPlayers}

Total Goals

{stats.totalGoals}

Total Assists

{stats.totalAssists}

Average Age

{formatNumber(stats.averageAge)}

{/* Top Performers */}
{/* Top Scorers */}

Top Scorers

{stats.topScorers.slice(0, 5).map((player, index) => (
{index + 1}.

{player.Player}

{player.Squad}

{player.Gls} goals

{formatNumber(player['Gls.1'], 2)} per 90

))}
{/* Top Assisters */}

Top Assisters

{stats.topAssisters.slice(0, 5).map((player, index) => (
{index + 1}.

{player.Player}

{player.Squad}

{player.Ast} assists

{formatNumber(player['Ast.1'], 2)} per 90

))}
{/* Filter Summary */}

Current View

Showing Players

{filteredPlayers.length}

Teams

{stats.teams.length}

Nations

{stats.nations.length}

); }; export default Dashboard;
